ature spaces. We\nalso obtain, under suitable conditions, dimension-free bounds of the optimal\ntransport cost in terms of entropy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Jul 2018 01:39:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2020 20:36:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 5 Jul 2020 01:56:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-07"}
